                "invention-title": [
                    "System for realizing low-carbon emission of coal-fired power plant by taking green hydrogen as carrier",
                    "一种以绿氢为载体的实现燃煤电厂低碳排放的系统"
                ]
            },
            "abstract": [
                {
                    "p": "The invention belongs to the technical field of hydrogen energy, and particularly relates to a system for realizing low-carbon emission of a coal-fired power plant by taking green hydrogen as a carrier. The system comprises a renewable energy system, an auxiliary power system, a coal-fired power generation system, a power grid, a water electrolysis hydrogen production system, a hydrogen storage system, a hydrogenation system, a hydrogen fuel cell system, a carbon dioxide capture system, a methanol synthesis system, an oxygen storage system, an air separation system, a nitrogen storage system, a synthesis ammonia system and a waste heat management system. The invention provides a system for realizing low carbon emission of a coal-fired power plant by taking green hydrogen as a carrier, which takes renewable energy hydrogen production as a core and is coupled with a hydrogen fuel cell power generation system, a hydrogen transportation system, a carbon dioxide capture system, a green hydrogen synthesis ammonia system and a carbon dioxide hydrogenation methanol production system. A large amount of carbon dioxide discharged by a traditional coal-fired power plant is converted into a green chemical product, so that low-carbon and zero-carbon emission of the coal-fired power plant is achieved, and a comprehensive solution is provided for the zero-carbonization process of an electric power system and the zero-carbonization process of fuel."
                },
                {
                    "p": "本发明属于氢能技术领域，特别涉及一种以绿氢为载体的实现燃煤电厂低碳排放的系统。本发明包括可再生能源系统、厂用电系统、燃煤发电系统、电网、水电解制氢系统、储氢系统、加氢系统、氢燃料电池系统、二氧化碳捕集系统、合成甲醇系统、储氧系统、空分系统、储氮系统、合成氨系统、余热管理系统。本发明提供了一种以绿氢为载体的实现燃煤电厂低碳排放的系统，以可再生能源制氢为核心，耦合氢燃料电池发电系统、氢交通系统、二氧化碳捕集系统、绿氢合成氨系统、二氧化碳加氢制甲醇系统，将传统燃煤电厂排放的大量二氧化碳转化为绿色化工产品，以实现燃煤电厂的低碳、零碳排放，为电力系统零碳化和燃料零碳化进程提供综合解决方案。"
                }
